{"tid":1178297,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會晤張建宗後未釋疑　美商會八問政府","createTime":"2019-05-30T09:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T10:45:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"28b412bc1814ce16ff11475a143c208b2028f5b4","tid":1178297,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/amcham-17_WqT23_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Famcham-17_WqT23_1200x0.png&h=4a51e981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n編按：政府強推《逃犯條例》修訂，美國商會今日向傳媒發新聞稿，稱在3月29日曾會見政務司司長張建宗，但商會認為修例仍然有太多不明確的地方，有必要修例通過之前向香港社會解釋清楚，又指香港未準備好，不明為何政府要急於修例。美國商會另向政府提出8項問題，包括質問為何要在低犯罪率的香港，冒著法治聲譽受損的風險修例。<br />\n<br />\n【文：香港美國商會】<br />\n<br />\nProposed Fugitive Offenders Ordinance <br />\n<br />\nHong Kong &ndash; May 30, 2019 &ndash; AmCham appreciated the opportunity to meet with Chief Secretary for Administration Matthew Cheung to explain our concerns about the Fugitive Offenders Ordinance on Wednesday March 29. The Chief Secretary said the government was keen to alleviate worries that the bill would have a negative impact on Hong Kong's status as an international business hub.  <br />\n<br />\nAmCham's Position on the Bill <br />\n<br />\nAmCham feels that there are too many uncertainties in fundamental sections of the proposed legislation that must be addressed and explained to the broader Hong Kong community before tabling the bill for passage by the Legislative Council. Hong Kong is not ready to see this bill passed, and we do not see why it should be rushed through when the loophole it seeks to address has existed for 20 years. We believe that for Hong Kong to remain a center of excellence for the rule of law and legal practice that due legislative process is followed. We have asked the Chief Secretary&rsquo;s office for answers to the following questions: <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/逃犯條例-會晤張建宗後未釋疑-美商會八問政府/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%AA%E9%87%8B%E7%96%91-%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E5%85%AB%E5%95%8F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%2F&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1ajakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=3b751a1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%AA%E9%87%8B%E7%96%91-%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E5%85%AB%E5%95%8F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%2F&h=9f3dfacc\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/逃犯條例-會晤張建宗後未釋疑-美商會八問政府/</a>"},{"pid":"ad605c59b2db008b4c9511b250077123058c97f4","tid":1178297,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"22de61b97a9d983631192a7b1237412f89b38739","tid":1178297,"uid":65604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:06:21.000Z","msg":"其實張建宗見到對方眼神已經知道有人開始動搖，但為免對方老尷所以唔開名住。"},{"pid":"727d79c7132396b0682ff1598fffb89b46e73b22","tid":1178297,"uid":11719,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"根本班官都唔清楚條條例，點同人講，一咪話無事無事，真係白痴先會信"},{"pid":"f10e097399807174ad6cfe242b5ba2a8a10c7a75","tid":1178297,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e38f2a8392562c3f2ec946ef937eb8dc54d70e","tid":1178297,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99c658269eb86c5ba7a5021c16bb01add6aa6f1","tid":1178297,"uid":103230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"其實最主要問題係冇人信你老共呀⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces